{"tid":2303034,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「韓國新垣結衣」有多美？日網友看過亦大讚：「超越本尊了！」","createTime":"2020-11-27T14:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T05:26:12.000Z","uid":79562,"like":4,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"307876d60d2c2a283028a8a39e1e6d64ca4fa709","tid":2303034,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T14:46:11.000Z","msg":"在日本土生土長的韓國女模Soyon，去年為時裝秀「關西Collection2019」走秀，知名度大漲，更有網友指出她外貌酷似日本女星新垣結衣，最近另有日本網友在「2ch」PO出她的火辣美照，並說「韓國的新垣結衣太可愛了」，讓網友也大讚「超越本尊了」、「根本不像，她更可愛」、「超越了新垣結衣，好不甘心啊」，但也有人一針見血地說：「你們只是著迷她的身材。」<br />\n<br />\nSoyon臉蛋清純可愛，卻有著魔鬼身材，也總是不吝惜秀出她33C、23、34的好身材，時常小露性感，或是扮成性感小野貓，引起日本網友喜愛，但近年日韓關係緊張，Soyon也收到一些日本網友的惡意回應，但她並不介意，表明依舊很喜歡日本，希望能在當地演藝圈努力開創屬於自己的一片天<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2020-11-25/656/20201125006767.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2020-11-25%2F656%2F20201125006767.jpg&h=cd94520f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hzEsYAyNSJWpOIA1OBkJaPXR2JgV9TDZpKhZ0dRFOe143FWA5dkRuX2JwfVs0GWI0IBZiCW4lPlswFjU7IEVu/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hzEsYAyNSJWpOIA1OBkJaPXR2JgV9TDZpKhZ0dRFOe143FWA5dkRuX2JwfVs0GWI0IBZiCW4lPlswFjU7IEVu%2Fw644&h=83030c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hcX-RwmIHPHcQKxRTWElDICp9PxgjRy90dB1taE9FYkNpHnkkKE93Qjx_a0RvE3spfh17FDcsJ0ZuHSwmfk53/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hcX-RwmIHPHcQKxRTWElDICp9PxgjRy90dB1taE9FYkNpHnkkKE93Qjx_a0RvE3spfh17FDcsJ0ZuHSwmfk53%2Fw644&h=60609b23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hTxIsqI6wC1d0CiNzPGl0AE5cCDhHZhhUEDxaSCtkVWMNP04ETG5BYlgPVGBdP0wJGjxMNFECEGYKPBsGGm9B/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hTxIsqI6wC1d0CiNzPGl0AE5cCDhHZhhUEDxaSCtkVWMNP04ETG5BYlgPVGBdP0wJGjxMNFECEGYKPBsGGm9B%2Fw644&h=c547b157&s={SIZE}\" />"